<plot>A documentary series exploring the lives of servants and masters in modern day society. The cameras follow the action for a period of two weeks. For the first week one family acts as the servants for the other family in the own home. For the second week the roles of the families are reversed.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?360533</url></doc>
